Note on underlying data:

The data in this repository is derived from publicly available sources:

  - World Bank Open Data (CC BY 4.0)
    https://data.worldbank.org

  - UNHCR Refugee Statistics (CC BY 4.0)
    https://www.unhcr.org/refugee-statistics

This license applies to the code and derived dataset in this repository.
The underlying source data remains subject to the terms of its original
providers as listed above.
